### 1. **Post Entity - Complete Field List**

**File Path:** `C:\projects\develop_blog\backend\devblog\devblog\src\main\java\met\ivan\devblog\entity\Post.java`

**Fields:**
- `id` (Long) - Primary key, auto-generated
- `title` (String, 255 chars, NOT NULL) - Post title
- `slug` (String, 300 chars, UNIQUE, NOT NULL) - URL-friendly identifier
- `contentMarkdown` (String, TEXT, NOT NULL) - Main content in markdown format
- `excerpt` (String, 300 chars, nullable) - Brief summary
- `status` (PostStatus enum, NOT NULL, default: DRAFT) - DRAFT or PUBLISHED
- `author` (User, ManyToOne, LAZY, NOT NULL) - Foreign key to author
- `category` (Category, ManyToOne, LAZY, nullable) - Foreign key to category
- `publishedAt` (Instant, nullable) - When published (set at publish time)
- `createdAt` (Instant, NOT NULL, immutable) - Creation timestamp
- `updatedAt` (Instant, NOT NULL) - Last update timestamp
- `version` (Long) - Optimistic locking version field

**Indexes:** slug, status, author_id (for query optimization)

