| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Query Params | Returns | Purpose |
|--------|----------|------|--------------|---------|---------|
| GET | `/api/posts` | Public | `category` (slug), `search` (text), `Pageable` (size=20 default) | `Page&lt;PostSummaryResponse&gt;` | List published posts, filter by category/search |
