| GET | `/api/posts/mine` | USER role | `status` (POST enum, optional), `Pageable` | `Page&lt;PostSummaryResponse&gt;` | List user's own posts with status filter |
| GET | `/api/posts/mine/{id}` | Authenticated | - | `PostResponse` | Get own post details |

